<li><a href="http://www.economist.com/research/Economics/alphabetic.cfm?LETTER=M#MONETARISM" class="external text" title="http://www.economist.com/research/Economics/alphabetic.cfm?LETTER=M#MONETARISM" rel="nofollow">Monetarism</a> from the Economics A-Z of <a href="/wiki/The_Economist" title="The Economist">The Economist</a></li>
</ul>
